The golden prospector legs are a cosmetic variant of the prospector legs obtained by using a star fragment on them, which costs 3,000 stardust from Dusuri's Star Shop.

Like its original variant, the legs grant 0.6% bonus Mining experience and is increased to 2.5% when wearing the full prospector kit.
